description:
West Village is proudly offering this spectacular luxurious apartment with panoramic rooftop views facing towards the Sydney CBD and Blue Mountains. Live in luxury and extravagance in an ideal location situated in the heart of Parramatta. State-of-the-art, resident-exclusive amenities for all residents to enjoy.

Conveniently located within 300 meters walking distance to Westfields and 200 meters to Parramatta Train Station, Arthur Phillip High school, Buses, Cafes and restaurants are all conveniently located within few minutes walking distance.

Perfect investment for First Home Buyer or New Investors in a thriving location. Experience nature and contemporary lifestyle, at the forefront of everyday living. Retirees who are seeking to downsize to a luxurious apartment, will certainly enjoy the perks of having stunning rooftop views with exclusive rooftop garden.

Internal Features:
- Luxury Furnishings
- Soft Closing Drawers
- Timber Floorboards
- Spacious Bedrooms
- Reasonable size of study
- Internal Laundry with Dryer
- Separate Large Pantry

Outgoings per quarter:
Strata Rate: Approximately $1,200 per quarter
Council Rate: $ 303.88
Water Rate: $166.82 plus usage
